msgstr "Visa alternativet filtrera resultat?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:148
msgid ""
"This allows a user to filter the members of the extended family by gender "
"and if they are alive or dead."
msgstr "Möjliggör filtrering utifrån kön och om levande eller död."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:153
msgid "Show filter options"
msgstr "Visa filteralternativ"

