#: resources/views/settings.phtml:214
msgid ""
"Count the members of the partner chains as members of the extended family?"
msgstr "Inkludera personer i partnerföljd i släktband ?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:216
msgid ""
"If you select \"no\", then the additional members in the partner chains will "
"not be counted to the total number of individuals in the extended family."
msgstr ""
"Om du väljer \"Nej\", så inkluderas inte personer i partnerföljd i "
"släktbandet."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:217
msgid ""
"And these persons and families will be not selected when a user decides to "
"copy the extended family to the clippings cart."
msgstr ""
"Dessa personer och familjer kommer inte heller inkluderas när en användare "
"kopierar släktbandet till urklippskorgen."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:218
msgid ""
"But even in this case, you can copy these persons and families to the "
"clippings cart by using a special menu topic of the custom module \"enhanced "
"clippings cart\": \"add partner chains for an individual\"."
msgstr ""
"Men det finns ett tillägg, \"Enhanced Clippings cart\", som möjliggör att ta "
"med även dessa personer och familjer till urklippskorgen."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:219
msgid ""
"This is only relevant if you have chosen in the above table, that the "
"partner chains should be shown as a part of the extended family."
msgstr ""
"Det här blir bara relevant om man valt att inkludera partnerföljder i "
"släktbanden, i inställningen här nedan."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:225
msgid "Include them"
msgstr "Inkludera dem"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:233
msgid "Show parameters of extended family part?"
msgstr "Visa parametrar för släktband?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:234
msgid ""
"Display of additional information for each part of the extended family, such "
"as the generation shift and the coefficient of relationship, which is a "
"measure of the degree of consanguinity."
msgstr ""
"Visning av ytterligare information för varje släktband, t.ex. "
"generationsavstånd och släktskapskoefficient i procent."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:239
msgid "Show parameters"
msgstr "Vis parametrar"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:247
msgid "Use the compact design?"
msgstr "Använd kompakt design?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:248
msgid ""
"The compact design only shows the name and life span for each person. The "
"enriched design also shows a photo (if this is activated for this tree) as "
"well as birth and death information."
msgstr ""
"Kompakt design visar bara namn och livslängd för varje person. Utökad design "
"visar också ett foto tillsammans med födelse och död."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:253
msgid "Use the compact design"
msgstr "Använd kompakt design"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:261
msgid "Show name of proband as short name or as full name?"
msgstr "Visa kort eller fullständigt namn på proband?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:262
msgid ""
"The short name is based on the probands Rufname or nickname. If these are "
"not available, the first of the given names is used, if one is given. "
"Otherwise the last name is used."
msgstr ""
"Kort namn baseras på probandets tilltalsnamn eller smeknamn. Om dessa "
"saknas, används första förnamnet om det finns. Annars används efternamnet."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:267
msgid "Show short name"
msgstr "Vis kort namn"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:275
msgid "How should place names be shown in event boxes?"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:276
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether event places are shown as full place names or "
"as abbreviated place names."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:281
msgid "Place name format"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:289
msgid "Show labels in special situations?"
msgstr "Visa etiketter i speciella situationer?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:290
msgid ""
"Labels (or stickers) are used for example for adopted persons or foster "
"children."
msgstr "Etiketter används t.ex. för adoptiv- eller fosterbarn."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:295
msgid "Show labels"
msgstr "Visa etiketter"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:303
msgid "Show relationship to the proband as mouse-over text?"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:304
msgid ""
"This shows the relationship of a person to the proband when the mouse "
"pointer is over the name."
msgstr ""

